ğŸ“Š Data Analysis & Visualization
Key Insights:
â€¢	Age 25â€“40 customers make the most purchases.

â€¢	Digital payments (PayPal, Credit Card) dominate successful transactions.

â€¢	Top 10 products generate 60% of total sales.

â€¢	Sales spike during Q4 (Octoberâ€“December).
